323
00:23:31.734 --> 00:23:34.774

324
00:23:39.934 --> 00:23:42.733
Cock-a-doodle-doo!

325
00:23:42.734 --> 00:23:46.054
Cock-a-doodle-doo!

326
00:23:47.855 --> 00:23:50.254
